  <li class="list-group-item">Step Three: Download a resource you need and leave a rating</li>
  <li class="list-group-item">You will be able to keep on downloading resources as often as you want as long as your ratio of uploaded resources divided by your 
                              downloaded resources is at least .75</li>

</ul>
  <p class="lead">
    <%= link_to "Sign up", signup_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
  </p>
</div>    



